data.description: $15,000 PRICE REDUCTION!!! Well maintained, upgraded, move in ready 3 bedroom + Den/BONUS ROOM, 2 bathroom, 2 car garage in Pecan Creek North within walking distance to Elementary School & Community Park. Open concept home offers, nice neutral interior paint & staggered laid tile throughout except in bedrooms where there is carpet, granite countertops, upgraded fixtures, Appliances & water heater are new within 3 years, spacious family room with surround sound, large master bedroom is split from bedrooms 2 & 3 by the large open Den/Bonus Room. Nice covered patio, with grass backyard with watering system and trees lined behind block wall for great shade & no neighbors behind for privacy. FLOATING SHELVES ON FAMILYROOM WALL DO NOT CONVEY!!! Buyer will need to contact Rural Metro for service
